CS 465 Team Contract

Communication:
We agree to meet every week on (day of week) from (time)  at (place) during the course project.
We agree to arrive on time for all team meetings and notify the group at least 24 hours in advance if we are unable to make it.
We agree to use (Slack/Discord) as a communication channel and actively participate in group discussions.
We agree to respond to communications from staff and fellow team members within _____ hours.

Work Distribution:
We agree to divide work fairly and contribute equally to all project deliverables.
We agree to complete assigned tasks by the date/time decided by the team.
We agree to spend a minimum of ___ hours per week working on the project.
We agree to maintain high-quality work that meets the teamâ€™s expectations.
We agree to inform our team members when we are unable to complete our assigned task at least _____ hours before the deadline.
We agree to catch up on missed work in future deliverables.

Team Etiquette:
We agree to treat everyone with respect and professionalism
We agree to be inclusive and ensure everyone gets a chance to speak/contribute during discussions related to the project.
We agree to make decisions by (consensus/majority?)
We agree to provide constructive feedback on each otherâ€™s work within 24 hours.
We agree to revise our work based on the feedback given by our team members.
We agree to support each other and ask for help if needed.
